We have a abstract product class called post, which has attributes like id, title, createdOn and pulishedOn and their methods.
We have multiple subclasses which extent this post like NewsPost, BlogPost and ProductPost
NewPost is a class that represents news articles that are published on the site with attributes like headLine and newsTime.
BlogPost is a class that represents articles that are published on the site with attributes like author and tags array.
create a simple factory for creation of different posts on website